Feature: Search
  In order to find a word definition
  As a website user
  I need to be able to search for a word

@javascript
Scenario: Search for a word that exists
    Given I am on "/wiki/Main_Page"
    When I fill in "search" with "Velociraptor"
    And I press "searchButton"
    Then I should see "an enlarged sickle-shaped claw"



Feature: Log in
In order to use website functionality
As a website user
I need to be able to log in

@javascript
Scenario: Log in with valid data
Given I am on “http://meego.drupalcompany.com/”
When I press “Log in”
And fill v.popovych+org11@internetdevels.ua in field E-mail or username
And fill “1” in field “Password”
Then I should see “Log out”
